The paper focuses on using deep reinforcement learning to train a vision-based navigation policy for autonomous flight in indoor environments. This falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO) as well as computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the paper addresses safety-critical domains, which could also place it under the category of systems and control (cs.SY).
